data.description: PRIME DEVELOPMENT OPPORTUNITY!  Located in this rapidly growing Southwest Medford neighborhood, this is a perfect opportunity for a small development project.  The house is well cared for and sits on the lot so that it could remain intact and up to 10 lots could be built around it.  Property is currently zoned as SFR-00, but could be zoned SFR-10. Buyer to do their own due diligence with the city.
